          "assignments": [
            {
              "id": "ai-prompt",
              "name": "aiPrompt",
              "value": "=Trending topics in India right now:\n{{ $json.topics.map((t, i) => (i+1) + \". [\" + t.source.toUpperCase() + \"] \" + t.title + (t.score ? \" (Score: \" + t.score + \")\" : \"\") + (t.viewCount ? \" (Views: \" + t.viewCount + \")\" : \"\")).join(\"\\n\") }}\n\nAnalyze these and create engaging social media content.",
